::'''Insighter:''' Guys, please be very, very careful of those thugs under Gray Bean Paste. We need to take them seriously.
::'''Insighter:''' Ah, it's you! It was you who sent me to that wicked teleporter! Because of you, I landed on my face and suffered for a long time!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I did? I can't remember anything.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500017005-->
:::'''Insighter:''' I can't believe you don't remember me! Have you forgotten about Lord Molten Cheese Tart too?
:::'''Insighter:''' You're a bad guy! How can you do this to us!?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm sorry for being too rough on you guys.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500017008-->
:::'''Insighter:''' Mwahaha, you just apologized to me! I didn't expect your noble self would be willing to do that!
:::'''Insighter:''' After all, you're Miss Ruan Mei's assistant &mdash; or should I say "deputy"?
:::'''Insighter:''' Since you've apologized, I'll forgive you!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_500017011-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500017011-->
::'''Insighter:''' Mwahaha, what a surprise to see you here! By the way, I have a little secret to share with you. Don't tell the other bad snacks...
::'''Insighter:''' Please stop addressing me as "Molten Cheese Tart" in public, not even "Honorable Lord Molten Cheese Tart".
::'''Insighter:''' Now, I'm called the "Insighter," I am one who is wise and well-composed. Please call me "Lord Insighter" or "The Wise Lord Insighter" in the future!
