::{{DIcon|Talk}} Why the sudden name change?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500017207-->
:::Molten Cheese Tart&mdash; nope, the one who identifies as Insighter, looks at you with a firm gaze.
:::'''Insighter:''' You taught me to be humble. Don't you remember that?
:::'''Insighter:''' Ruan Mei admires you, so I'll listen to your advice and be someone like you!
:::'''Insighter:''' The impression "Molten Cheese Tart" has left on everyone is set too deep to be changed, not even by a genius like me! So, I decided to get a new name and start afresh!
:::'''Insighter:''' As long as my changes are significant enough, Ruan Mei will definitely be moved by my effort!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
